@@TJvCustomStaticText.ShowAccelChar
Summary
  Enables accelerator characters.
Description
  If ShowAccelChar is true, an ampersand in the component’s Caption text appears as an underline and
  makes the character after it into an accelerator key. If ShowAccelChar is false, ampersands appear
  as ampersands.

