@@TJvCustomStaticText.HotTrack
Summary
  Specifies whether the control is highlighted when the mouse passes over it.
Description
  Set HotTrack to true to provide visual feedback about which item is under the mouse; the font
  specified by HotTrackFont is used for the control's text. When HotTrack is false, there is no
  visual feedback when the mouse passes over this control.
See Also
  TJvExWinControl.OnMouseEnter, TJvExWinControl.OnMouseLeave

