@@TJvCustomStaticText
Summary
  TJvCustomStaticText is the base class for TJvStaticText.
Description
  TJvCustomStaticText is the base class for TJvStaticText, a windowed control that displays text on a
  form. This component functions like TStaticText, but supports extended features such as hot
  tracking.

